    "body": "@huwentao1, you are getting this error because you are importing the HRE in your config, but it hasn't been constructed yet, as your config is being defined.\r\n\r\nInstead of doing this\r\n\r\n```\r\nimport {ethers,  tasks,  upgrades } from \"hardhat\"\r\n```\r\n\r\nuse the `HRE` instance that your tasks get as argument.\r\n\r\nAlso, you don't need to `require` scripts like this `require(\"./scripts/deploy\")`. It will probably break everything, possibly with the same error.",
